commit b8f75b6a9f131c7a975cd5e66174166f45189848
Author: SCAR <floppypancakes4u@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Jul 13 21:43:31 2026 -0500

    Fix mission flow and death loot handling
    
    This hardens several gameplay paths that were desyncing or crashing clients. Missions now advance deliver objectives correctly across sequences, support fail/abandon, respect race/class offer gates, restore mission cargo on login, and send proper objective state/client resync packets for patrol and turn-in flows.
    
    It also adds server-side map-prop ram damage with delayed corpse despawn, rewrites death loot to use retail-style gear/junk/consumable/commodity tracks, sends fuller destroy/death packets for creatures and vehicles, tightens vehicle equipment and wheelset ghost wiring, and adds configurable loot/log diagnostics plus broad regression coverage.

